OL,3,C25 fatalities linked to fires in 2024
OL,5,FThere were 25 fatalities in Ireland
OL,6,Fdue to fire incidents in 2024,
OL,7,Faccording to official statistics
OL,8,Fpublished on Monday.
OL,10,FChimneys, flues, hot ashes and soot
OL,11,Fwere the top causes of fires recorded
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FBlazes started due to malicious intent
OL,15,Fand rubbish burning also featured
OL,16,Fhighly in the figures published by the
OL,17,FDepartment of Housing and Local
OL,18,FGovernment.
