OL,3,C25 fatalities linked to fires in 2024
OL,5,FBrigades attended almost 20,000 fires
OL,6,Fin 2024 across various locations in
OL,7,Fthe Republic, including domestic
OL,8,Fbuildings, industrial facilities,
OL,9,Fmotor vehicles, forest and grassland
OL,10,Fareas, outdoor rubbish sites, as well
OL,11,Fas ships and aircraft.
OL,13,FWithin homes, fires caused by
OL,14,Felectrical wiring and electrical
OL,15,Fequipment, cooking and heating all
OL,16,Ffeatured as causes of fire.
OL,18,FOf the 25 deaths last year, 21 were
OL,19,Fpeople aged 55 or over.
