OL,3,C25 fatalities linked to fires in 2024
OL,5,FKeith Leonard, national director for
OL,6,Ffire and emergency management said:
OL,7,F"My condolences to the families and
OL,8,Ffriends of people who have lost their
OL,9,Flives to fires."
OL,11,FHe added: "I hope that publishing this
OL,12,Fdata will remind all of us of the need
OL,13,Ffor vigilance and the importance of
OL,14,Ffire prevention and safety measures."
