OL,3,C25 fatalities linked to fires in 2024
OL,5,FMr Leonard encouraged the public to
OL,6,Fthink of older neighbours and
OL,7,Frelatives, adding: "The next time you
OL,8,Fare in their homes, check that they
OL,9,Fhave a working smoke alarm ` the most
OL,10,Fimportant piece of fire safety
OL,11,Fequipment for the home."
OL,13,FThe national directorate for fire and
OL,14,Femergency management advises at least
OL,15,Fone smoke alarm is fitted on every
OL,16,Flevel of a home, which should be
OL,17,Ftested weekly to ensure it can be
OL,18,Fheard in the bedrooms. The expiry date
OL,19,Fshould also be checked.
