OL,5,FThe directorate said it is possible to
OL,6,Fdie from smoke inhalation within three
OL,7,Fminutes and "the sound of a smoke
OL,8,Falarm is the sound that could save
OL,9,Fyour life".
OL,11,FIt also advised people to have an
OL,12,Fescape plan in the event of the smoke
OL,13,Falarm sounding, adding: "The simplest
OL,14,Froute is generally the best way out".
